<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>369</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ zuì ài tīng, yé sū de gù shì, tā de gù shì gǎi biàn wǒ yī shēng,
 wǒ yě zuì ài jiǎng, yé sū de gù shì, néng bǎ chén shuì zhī sǐ de rén huàn xǐng,
 a! yé sū, wàn guó chuán sòng, nǐ de cí ài wú qióng, shí zì jià wèi zhèng,
 méi yǒu qiáng lǐ qiáng wài, dōu zài hé yī zhōng, nǐ shì wǒ men yǒng yuǎn de shēng mìng.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ zuì ài tīng yé sū de gù shì 迦南369</title>
</song>